metadata.name: Jatnna 1/1
metadata.description:
An impression of words and syntax, reminiscent of the natural language system of glyphs. A dream transcribed. Deformed with intention, enticing in its recognition. Worlds assembled through functional text. Blue washed crop denim jacket, saffron yellow draped knot long sleeve shirt, soft wool beret, translucent sparkling glass art earrings.

Synth Graph: a center front view, close up, 2020, photograph of a beautiful female model wearing a yellow jacket, mini skirt, blue lipstick, cute yellow purses, crystal earrings and a bandana, walking down Manhattan in the 1990s, highly detailed. Sampler: klms, steps: 70, scale: 10.
